javascript is dynamically typed language 
the data type of a variable by element value in it . it can be changed with value . 
changing one data type to anther datatype iscalled "type casting" there are two type of type casting. implicit and explicit 
implicit without external force it converts one data type to another 
explicit we need force to convert one data type to another

there are two classification of datatype in javascript 

1.primitive data type 
2.
i.number : number is data type assigined to any numerical value 
eg: 5,5.369
ii. string : string is a collection of characters.strong can be respresented by ' or "  
eg : 'raj',"pavan" 
ii.boolean : it is used to declare true or false. true is 1 false is 0 
iv. undefined : it is used to store "undefined" data 
v.null : it is used to store "null" data 

2.non-primitive data type 
i.function 
ii.Arrays 
iii.objects



i.number : any numerical data is number , to find datatype of a element we can  se type of operator 
numbers have some default 
